General.Name: Imperial Equities Inc.
General.Description: Imperial Equities Inc. engages in the acquisition, development, redevelopment, leasing, and sale of commercial, industrial, and agricultural properties primarily in Edmonton and Alberta, Canada. Imperial Equities Inc. was incorporated in 1998 and is headquartered in Edmonton, Canada.
